summary: Completed comprehensive E2E testing of Mafi D hip-hop artist website. Backend APIs working perfectly (100% success rate). Frontend pages load correctly with all required content. Critical navigation issue identified with announcement banner overlay blocking clicks.

ui_bugs.issue: Banner overlay blocks navigation clicks - users cannot click nav links when banner is visible
ui_bugs.impact: Prevents navigation between pages, major UX issue

passed_tests: All 8 pages load correctly via direct URL access
Music page Spotify and Apple Music embeds present
About page contains Central District and East Union Street mentions
Contact form submission works (form resets after success)
Email signup form works (form resets after success)
Announcement banner countdown timer displays correctly
Banner close button works when clicked with force
All page content loads as expected
action_item_for_main_agent: Fix announcement banner z-index/overlay issue preventing navigation clicks. The banner intercepts pointer events making nav links unclickable. This is a critical UX bug that blocks basic site navigation.
